{"type":"answer","id":29855,"parentType":"question","parentId":1204,"uid":6405,"contents":"政治立场坐标（左翼&lt;-&gt;右翼）0.9，<br>\n<br>\n经济立场坐标（左翼&lt;-&gt;右翼）0.5，<br>\n<br>\n文化立场坐标（保守&lt;-&gt;自由）1.2，<br>\n<br>\nX坐标反映政治观念，负值为左(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Authoritarianism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">独裁主义</a>)，正值为右(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Libertarianism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自由意志主义</a>)。<br>\n<br>\nY坐标反映经济观念，负值为左(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">共产主义</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Collectivism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">集体主义</a>)，正值为右(<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neoliberalism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新自由主义</a>)。<br>\n<br>\nZ坐标反映社会文化观念，负值为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Conservatism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">保守主义</a>，正值为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Liberalism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">自由主义</a>。<br>\n<br>\n政治立场坐标<br>\n1.1<br>\n<br>\n文化立场坐标<br>\n1<br>\n<br>\n经济立场坐标<br>\n0.3<br>\n[url=https://www.zuobiao.me/zuobiao2015/index.php/survey/index][/url]<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n我这是右派还是左派啊？<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://blog.xavierskip.com/2015-05-03-politics-coordinate/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.xavierskip.com/2015-05-03-politics-coordinate/</a>&nbsp;对“中国政治坐标系测试”进行的数据分析","date":"2019-07-15","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":1}